        {
            "title": "澤連斯基稱與美國特使威特科夫和庫什納進行了「非常好的」談話",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 澤連斯基周四表示，他與美國特使史蒂夫·威特科夫和賈裡德·庫什納就結束俄羅斯對烏克蘭的戰爭進行了「非常好的談話」。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">這位烏克蘭總統在X發帖稱：「我們討論了正在進行的工作的一些實質性細節。其中有一些很好的想法，能夠推動達成共同成果，並實現持久和平。」</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">推薦閱讀：俄羅斯將尋求修改美國最新提出的和平計畫 將其視為進一步談判的起點</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">澤連斯基感謝了威特科夫和川普女婿庫什納的「建設性方針」和「高強度工作」，並表示希望這些討論成為推動衝突走向和平的又一步。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-ededba5c-d045-3edf-8b1e-2727d63e70b2-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">白宮尚未就澤連斯基的帖子作出回應。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">俄方發言人Peskov周四對俄羅斯媒體表示，克里姆林宮正在審查特使Dmitriev呈遞給普丁的信息。此前Dmitriev周末在邁阿密與美方舉行了會談。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題Zelenskiy Says He Had ‘Very Good’ Talks With Witkoff, Kushner</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">--聯合報導 Hadriana Lowenkron、Yuliya Fedorinova.</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2025 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E6%BE%A4%E9%80%A3%E6%96%AF%E5%9F%BA%E7%A8%B1%E8%88%87%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E7%89%B9%E4%BD%BF%E5%A8%81%E7%89%B9%E7%A7%91%E5%A4%AB%E5%92%8C%E5%BA%AB%E4%BB%80%E7%B4%8D%E9%80%B2%E8%A1%8C%E4%BA%86-%E9%9D%9E%E5%B8%B8%E5%A5%BD%E7%9A%84-%E8%AB%87%E8%A9%B1-173531096.html",
            "pub_date": "2025-12-26 03:10:46",
            "source": "yahoo_finance_asia",
